---
title: Herby Chicken & Roast Sesame Pumpkin Salad with Garlicky Almond Crumb & Mayonnaise
description: Make way for this hearty main meal salad in your dinner rotation. With mildly spiced herby chicken and a dollop of
creamy mayo, this plate of bountiful, sweet roasted pumpkin and beetroot will change the way you look at veggies!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
